.agents/skills/skill-creator

# Repo-wide junk/dependency hygiene (consolidated from nested .gitignore files —
# there should be exactly one .gitignore in this repo, at the root).
# Previously: .agents/skills/audio-album-creator/scripts/.gitignore had
# .venv/ and __pycache__/ scoped to that one directory; these patterns cover
# the same ground repo-wide so any future skill with a local venv is
# protected without needing its own nested .gitignore.
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
**/.venv/
**/.DS_Store
